name: PixelFem #7 - Emily Eavis
description:
Emily Eavis has been working behind-the-scenes on the UK's (and possibly the world's) biggest music festival for more than two decades - Glastonbury. Working in a male dominated industry, Emily is constantly pushing for 50/50 male/female representation at her festival.

✺This work is part of PixelFems, an evolving project on the Tezos blockchain celebrating iconic women from the past and present✺
